{"tid":2176823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者朋友 麻煩可唔可以唔用再主動用'發放信息\"呢種蝗語?","createTime":"2020-08-27T10:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T06:16:48.000Z","uid":47659,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d5f23ce59c1388c8968d4b195f1c6d4b1944dc2e","tid":2176823,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:13:17.000Z","msg":"各位記者朋友, 你地好多都係受過浸大同其他新聞系名校教育<br />\n中文程度想必一定不下於小弟<br />\n<br />\n但最近都觀察到你地出新聞稿同聲明, 好多時都可能無意夾雜蝗語<br />\n例如&quot;發放不實信息&quot;呢句說話 我可以斷言一定有傳統中文詞語可以表達, <br />\n例如可以用&quot;發放不實資料&quot;, 發放不實資訊&quot;等等<br />\n<br />\n捍衛中文抗拒蝗語入侵, 好多時都係靠你地新聞界朋友把關<br />\n希望可以考慮改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e9f7074809c3b509611269ed1f4d90f45efded","tid":2176823,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98df4226ea7458ebfe755536e5f098055f9e1463","tid":2176823,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cab37aa120a54930082a42e19c065d2013c6c36","tid":2176823,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:16:30.000Z","msg":"欲先毀滅一個民族 一定先毀滅語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67c94e97c2dc68377ab64f2a89aa37bafe82901","tid":2176823,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0